# 🛑 GLOBAL DENY: Ignore everything by default
*

# ✅ ALLOW-LIST: Essential configuration and documentation
!.gitignore
!README.md
!.env.example

# ✅ ALLOW-LIST: Permit directory traversal
!*/

# ✅ ALLOW-LIST: Compose files and YAML configurations
!**/*.yml
!**/*.yaml

# 🛑 RE-IGNORE: Ensure no data or secrets sneak in via allowed extensions
**/.env
**/data/**
**/logs/**
**/backups/**
**/postgres_data/**
**/postgres_backups/**
**/*.sql
**/*.log
